    }, {
      "air_date" : "2026-01-12",
      "description" : "With advice from Sero and Siu, Mike and Hugh improve little by little and deepen their friendship as fellow junior workers. Meanwhile, Sero is playing pachinko on his day off when he gets a call from Siu saying, \"Get here in five minutes.\" He rushes to a corner of the city only to find...\nSource: Crunchyroll",
      "episode_id" : 305998,
      "length" : 25,
      "number" : 2,
      "recap" : false,
      "resources" : {
