      "type" : "REGULAR"
    }, {
      "air_date" : "2026-01-19",
      "description" : "\"So our company president is unusual then!\" What truth about the beautiful company president, Hela, will Mike`s innocent comment reveal? And why do full-time employee Noe and Sero always snarl at each other? Then, when Sero, who is usually so passionate about his work, takes some time off without giving a reason...\nSource: Crunchyroll",
      "episode_id" : 305999,
      "length" : 25,
      "number" : 3,
      "recap" : false,
      "resources" : {
        "CRUNCHY_ROLL" : [ "GE00366331JAJP" ]
