        "title" : "Episode 4"
      } ],
      "type" : "REGULAR"
    }, {
      "air_date" : "2026-02-02",
      "description" : "Hugh frets over a report for his Modern Torture Studies course. On the advice of his friend Las, he decides to talk to Sero and the others about it. When he does, he suddenly finds himself in the First Heart-Pounding Torture Quiz Tournament! Then, on another day, all the Spirytus employees and part-time workers head to the beach together! Siu suspects that Hela might be up to something.\nSource: Crunchyroll",
      "episode_id" : 307244,
