      } ],
      "type" : "REGULAR"
    }, {
      "air_date" : "2026-02-09",
      "description" : "After finishing up a book that he`d been having trouble writing, Mike enjoys cleaning after a torture session. Then, a cleaner named Rische shows up. Rische, wearing full protective gear and a gas mask, is quite shy, but seems interested in Mike. Later, a torture request and kill request overlap in a double booking. Manika, the contract killer who shows up for the job, is Sero`s ex-girlfriend.\nSource: Crunchyroll",
      "episode_id" : 307245,
