        "title" : "Episode 6"
      } ],
      "type" : "REGULAR"
    }, {
      "air_date" : "2026-02-16",
      "description" : "When Sero sees a university pamphlet for Modern Torture Studies in his younger brother Luc`s room, he feels shaken. Before he`s able to find a good way to bring it up, he and Luc head into town to do some shopping where they happen to run into Siu. On a different day, Siu takes Sero to see his daughters` elementary school recital. Siu fits in with the mothers there to a truly amazing extent.\nSource: Crunchyroll",
