    }, {
      "air_date" : "2026-02-23",
      "description" : "When a villain faints before he can be tortured, Izua, a doctor, rushes to his aid. While he`s there, he says he`ll check on Hela and Siu, too. Later, Mike injurs his finger and Merim, a nurse, treats it for him. Merim is a girl who speaks through her stuffed toy, Amumu, and...\nSource: Crunchyroll",
